OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775952175
OL,3,CPrince Harry facing defamation claim
OL,4,Cfrom his former charity Sentebale
OL,6,FThe charity Prince Harry founded to
OL,7,Fhelp children orphaned by HIV/Aids in
OL,8,FSouthern Africa is suing him.
OL,10,FHigh Court records show that the Duke
OL,11,Fof Sussex is a defendant in a libel or
OL,12,Fslander claim.
OL,14,FThe claim also names his long-time
OL,15,Ffriend and mentor, Mark Dyer.
OL,17,FIn March 2025, Harry issued a joint
OL,18,Fstatement with Prince Seeiso of
OL,19,FLesotho with whom he had founded the
OL,20,Fcharity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
