OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775952175
OL,3,CPrince Harry facing defamation claim
OL,4,Cfrom his former charity Sentebale
OL,6,FThey announced they had taken the
OL,7,F"devastating" decision to step down as
OL,8,Fpatrons of the charity to support the
OL,9,Fboard of trustees who had also
OL,10,Fresigned.
OL,12,FThey cited a dispute with the charity
OL,13,Fchair, Dr Sophie Canduka, over her
OL,14,Fmanagement of Sentebale and its funds.
OL,16,FThe trustees had previously asked Dr
OL,17,FChanduka to resign as they had
OL,18,Fconcerns about her leadership style
OL,19,Fand the direction in which she was
OL,20,Ftaking the charity.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
