FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775952175
OL,3,CPrince Harry facing defamation claim
OL,4,Cfrom his former charity Sentebale
OL,6,FFor her part, Dr Chanduka accused
OL,7,FPrince Harry of "harassment and
OL,8,Fbullying at scale" and claimed Harry
OL,9,Fwanted to use the charity as a "PR
OL,10,Fmachine" for his wife Meghan.
OL,12,FHarry founded charity Sentebale in
OL,13,F2006 with Prince Seeiso of Lesotho to
OL,14,Fhelp young people and children in
OL,15,Fsouthern Africa, particularly those
OL,16,Fliving with HIV and Aids.
OL,18,FOnline papers lodged at the High Court
OL,19,Fshow list the case as "Sentebale v
OL,20,FDuke of Sussex and another".
OL,26,@oD@QOUpD@RO]qD@`OUrD@HO]{D@WOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
