OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775952175
OL,3,CPrince Harry facing defamation claim
OL,4,Cfrom his former charity Sentebale
OL,6,FIt lists the case as being filed on 24
OL,7,FMarch 2026 under a case type described
OL,8,Fas "Media and Communication - Part 7
OL,9,FClaim - Defamation Libel and Slander".
OL,11,FThe Claimant is listed as "Sentebale"
OL,12,Fand the two defendants names are "Duke
OL,13,Fof Sussex, Prince Harry" and "Dyer,
OL,14,FMark".
OL,16,FThe Charity Commission opened an
OL,17,Finquiry after the claims became public
OL,18,Fand conducted a four-month
OL,19,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@qD@eO]sD@[OUsD@eO]tD@bOUuD@XO]uD@^OUvD@
OL,26,AEO]
