OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775952175
OL,3,CPrince Harry facing defamation claim
OL,4,Cfrom his former charity Sentebale
OL,6,FIn August last year, it found no
OL,7,Fevidence of "widespread or systemic
OL,8,Fbullying or harassment, including
OL,9,Fmisogyny or misogynoir at the charity"
OL,10,Fas Dr Chanduka had alleged.
OL,12,FNor did it find any evidence of 'over-
OL,13,Freach' by either the chair or the Duke
OL,14,Fof Sussex as patron.
OL,16,FBut the Commission did acknowledge the
OL,17,F"strong perception of ill treatment
OL,18,Ffelt by a number of parties to the
OL,19,Fdispute".
OL,26,@qD@fO]{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
