CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775952175
OL,3,CPrince Harry facing defamation claim
OL,4,Cfrom his former charity Sentebale
OL,6,FAnd the regulator identified
OL,7,F"mismanagement," including a lack of
OL,8,Fclear policies for resolving disputes.
OL,10,FThe Charity Commission criticised both
OL,11,Fsides, Prince Harry's and Dr
OL,12,FChanduka's, for allowing the dispute
OL,13,Fto "play out in the media", which had
OL,14,F"severely impacted the charity's
OL,15,Freputation".
OL,17,FITV News have reached out to Prince
OL,18,FHarry for comment.
OL,20,FThis is a breaking news story and will
OL,21,Fbe updated soon...
